uploads/
*.log
logs/
coverage/
.nyc_output/
tmp/
tmpaudit/

# --- Editor / OS -------------------------------------------------------------
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
.idea/
.vscode/*
!.vscode/extensions.json
*.swp
*~

# --- Client-facing commercial material ---------------------------------------
# Proposals, pricing and the pitch deck for the Aesthetics Clinic engagement.
# This repo is public: anything here is indexable and cached even after deletion,
# so the client's commercial terms stay local. Engineering docs (*.md) DO ship —
# they are the security and safety write-ups the code refers to.
docs/*.pdf
docs/*.docx
docs/annexure/
docs/*.png

# Commercial markdown/HTML — a naive "*.pdf" glob misses these, and they are the
# most sensitive things in the tree: the client proposal, competitor research,
# pricing and the pitch deck.
docs/clinic-proposal-faisalabad.md
docs/aesthetic-clinic-management-system-plan.md
docs/competitor-intelligence.md
docs/product-expansion-saas-strategy.md
docs/health-platform-master-plan.md
docs/research-and-plan-improvements.md
docs/health-os-deck.html
docs/admin-dashboard-mockup.html

# What DOES ship from docs/: the engineering record the code points at —
# security-rls-bypass-finding.md, dermatology-safety-review.md,
# specialty-packs-build-specs.md, specialty-packs-plan.md, and the
# architecture/colour references.

# Python bytecode from the safety suites
__pycache__/
*.pyc

# Deployment env (real values, never committed)
.env.prod
